{"tid":2221601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗12位手足之外 希望大家都唔好忘記佢","createTime":"2020-09-28T13:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T13:56:20.000Z","uid":153644,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c50b58bed5b8e3bc0d1bbd71867b66acc70fe0","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"就係<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span><br />\n嘅宗旨啊！<br />\n<br />\n見依家風氣咩都屌一餐<br />\nLunch 哥又屌<br />\n粉嶺手足又割<br />\n運動初期我地經常掛有嘴邊嘅<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化</span>去咗邊？<br />\n希望大家謹記點解我地當初以手足相稱<br />\n有人想出黎維持熱度 比佢做<br />\n有人想打國際線  無問題<br />\n街頭戰我地無可否認係短期內做唔到<br />\n何必再自己人互屌<br />\n只會比對家笑9我地<br />\n<br />\n祝大家<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">武運昌隆</span></span>"},{"pid":"62d1df676cbd0fa54cbf7724d875529276aefc68","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"推你上去"},{"pid":"558ae29f668612eed8a1f91df08dc981d97c07b3","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"手法可以唔認同 但係每一個都係手足"},{"pid":"dac0a8bb2b4c2eb6637c828fca5da62515222275","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">不割！</span>"},{"pid":"f0d5bf3d52700e82ca688f70b3a1a234d3223c57","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7b56158bac075a7a198f5595cb93cff352862ba","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"d3ba9a45f267b0d95aefeefbae1d1ed56e012b47","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f5b6e09f373a9abf954542765bd078dd48fb04c6","tid":2221601,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-2